    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四下手",
        "旗牌",
        "李洪基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将遇良才，棋逢对手，越令人豪气频添，把精神抖擞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺李洪基。俺奉了父王的将令，攻打岱州。那总兵周遇吉，他将人马扎在城外，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "排成犄角之势，吾军不能近前，此乃以主代客。前者与他交战，他的枪法，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "神出鬼入，不下与俺，难以招架。俺只得诈败而走，等他前来追赶与吾，暗放"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "飞刀前去斩他。又被他接去，反来斩俺。幸亏吾的坐骑千里驹，名曰闪电光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时若是迟了一步，定被他伤了俺的性命。自从父王与俺改名洪基，名字应了"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年号。只是俺叔父一支虎，有些妒忌与俺。若是招降此人，作为心腹，吾的天"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下稳稳。我今与他随机应变，同一事也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁，大王命你带领了精兵数十万，大战周遇吉，不可迟误。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王又有令前来，命俺前去大战周遇吉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四兵卒、四下手自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起兵迎敌者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（滴溜子） 催铁骑，催铁骑，如云骤，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挽金戈，挽金戈，如霜，光溜溜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各显威，神惊鬼愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基带马。〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "旗牌→李洪基",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "李洪基→四下手",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "四下手→李洪基",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
