    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉",
        "四小军",
        "李洪基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。四小军、四上手引周遇吉同上，同站门。四兵卒、四下手、李洪基同上。会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！马前来的，可是周将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惜你这般的大英雄威武，也算天下间一筹好汉。只是你生于末世，未逢明主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基吓，李洪基吓！俺周遇吉呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺堂堂帝统御中州，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸿图四海全收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是你主弱臣勇，将见败亡耳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺的圣上呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比尨尧舜功德茂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少什么稷契夔名胄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谅你一旅之师，际得什么事，为人也要见机而行，才称得起英雄好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺周遇吉呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠和孝，平身自守，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身和命笑浮沤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你昂昂气宇恁风流，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更艺勇可称琼玖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若倾心归顺，俺和你结为昆弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真果是，云龙风虎金兰友，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保毕世恩荣化胄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得多言，看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若如此行之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀头丧身家尽休，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄骨弃荒丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉 （急三枪） 俺心如铁，意如石，胆如斗，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任你随何口，说不转寸心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基 （急三枪） 莫待钟鸣漏尽，到山水穷头，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "灾星透，便欲悔悔无由。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小军、四兵卒自两边分下。周遇吉、李洪基同对抢，同亮架子，同开打，同下。四上手、四下手同开打，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同下。李洪基上，周遇吉杀上，李洪基败下。四小军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基走了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "追！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、四小军同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李洪基→周遇吉",
