    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉",
        "四小军",
        "李洪基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四兵卒、四下手、李洪基同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了吓，罢了吓！他的枪法十分厉害，这便怎么处？有了，等他到来，俺与他"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对刀可以取胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，杀上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小军、四上手、周遇吉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将军，为将者十八般武艺，件件皆能。你的枪法，不足为奇。你与俺对刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀乃军家要事，怎么不知！就与你对刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（急三枪） 披风泼雪猛如彪，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万丈寒光飞骤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边风声频吼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干羽振舞阶溜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉、李洪基",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，看刀伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉、李洪基",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、李洪基同换刀。四小军、四兵卒自两边分下。周遇吉、李洪基同开打，同对刀，同下。四上手、"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉、李洪基",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下手同开打，同下。李洪基上，周遇吉杀上，李洪基败下。四小军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小军",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李洪基又败走了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "追！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、四小军同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
