    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉",
        "李洪基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四兵卒、四下手、李洪基同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了吓，罢了吓！俺的刀法，数年以来，并无人对手。他的刀法，也不输俺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小军、四上手、周遇吉同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将军，你我马上武艺，彼此皆知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要怎样战法？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当初张飞与马超步战，杨再兴与庚丙文步战。俺如今与你比拳步战，若胜你不"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和你较拳纵飞演，比进步，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且往。俺与他交战，怎奈他的马骤如飞。如今反要与俺步战，此乃是天赐我成"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待要撼天山穿云斗海蛟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李洪基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将军，今日英雄遇英雄，好汉遇好汉，只可阵上赌输赢，不可暗箭伤人，方"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺平生，正直待人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狻猊摆尾下山头，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周遇吉、李洪基同下马，同起打。众人自两边分下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "李洪基→周遇吉",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "周遇吉→李洪基",
