    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周遇吉",
        "四上手",
        "四龙套",
        "龙套甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同上。〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位请了。元帅对李洪基交战，你我前去帮忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李洪基上，周遇吉上，李洪基、周遇吉同开打，周遇吉擒住李洪基。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉 （三笑） 呵呵，呵呵呵，哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将，将他的营盘闪电光抢过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启元帅：闪电光抢过来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，记功领赏。摆队进关。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小军、四上手自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜元帅，天神威武，擒此巨寇，威震华夷，小将等不胜忻贺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小丑虽擒，大逆尚存，何喜何贺？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看此子虽然年幼，英勇非常，何不亲解其缚，劝他降顺，岂不是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，你们哪里晓得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 他狼心野性岂驯柔，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暂降伏终成仇寇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（夹白） 若留在关内呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 反贼内外难防守，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，加恩放回去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周遇吉 （煞尾） 纵猛虎归山差谬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅如何处治？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官听令：那闯贼知我擒他爱子，必然统领大兵，前来劫夺。这场厮杀非比"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小可，我军当预先准备，吩咐阵前，多排鹿角，广布蒺藜，头层藤牌手，二层"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "火炮手，三层弩弓手，第四层长枪手，第五层攒箭手，必须人人奋勇，个个当"
        },
        {
          "character": "周遇吉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先，国家兴亡，在此一阵成功，奏凯论功升赏。众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 当一纶香饵在钩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要把鳌鱼钓，方得海波休！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
